  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink243-kilavi"> tāy uṭai yaṟiyāmai kūṟit tōḻi veṟi vilakkiyatu.   </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> Speaking of mother’s ignorance and thwarting the Veṟi ritual.
  
          
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink243">
<l>kaṟivaḷar cilampiṟ kaṭavuṭ pēṇi</l>
<l>yaṟiyā vēlaṉ veṟiyeṉak kūṟu</l>
<l>matumaṉaṅ koḷkuvai yaṉaiyivaḷ</l>
<l>putumalar maḻaikkaṇ pulampiya nōykkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Mother,</l>
        <l rend="space">for the pain</l>
        <l>in which her rain-eyes,</l>
        <l>[like] new blossoms,</l>
        <l>became lonely,</l>
        <l rend="space">you would consider in your mind</l>
        <l>what the Vēlaṉ says — “Veṟi” —</l>
        <l rend="space">[that Vēlaṉ who,]</l>
        <l>cherishing the lord</l>
        <l>of the mountain slopes</l>
        <l>where pepper grows,</l>
        <l rend="space">[remains] ignorant.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
